replies.txt_content:
World bw2 is a duplicate of another world and has been prevented from loading. Please delete the uid.dat file from bw2's world directory if you want to be able to load the duplicate world.

名字为 bw2 的世界重复了!!
你改个名字导入!
如果你想导入两个名字都是bw2 的世界, 那就去 bw2 这个文件夹吧 uid.dat 文件删了
不过不建议这样.

我建议你把 world/bw2 这个文件夹改名, 然后把 uid.dat 删了, 然后再导入.
